Package msquerybuilderbackend.business

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlertBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the entity Alert.
    AttributeTypes
    Class which contains method to check types if their value is from the given type and throws an execution if nots
    CategoryBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the entity Category
    ExpertQueryBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the entity ExpertQueryJsonObject in the application (ExpertQuery in the neo4j database)
    NodeTypeBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the Nodetypes in the neo4j database
    QueryBuilderBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the entity QueryBuilder in the application and QueryBuilderJsonStringObject in the neo4j database
    QueryBuilderWriterBusiness
    Class for building the neo4j queryString of the QueryBuilder Object
    RelationshipTypeBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the Relationshiptypes in the neo4j database
    UserBusiness
    Class for all activities with neo4j database regarding the entity User and its authorities
